sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Class Edit Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open create/update class page
    UI->>LW: mount(class)
    LW->>DB: Load class (if existing) + institutes
    DB-->>LW: Existing values and options
    LW-->>UI: Render class form

    User->>UI: Choose institute
    UI->>LW: updatedInstituteId(value)
    LW->>DB: Query campus and programme options
    DB-->>LW: Filtered options
    LW-->>UI: Re-render dependent selects

    User->>UI: Save form
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert/update class
    DB-->>LW: Persisted class
    LW-->>UI: Success toast (new: redirect to edit page)
